Spells per Day	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.AcolyteOfTheSkinClassFeatures.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:At each even-numbered level, an acolyte of the skin gains new spells per day (and spells known, if applicable) as if he had also gained a level in a spellcasting class to which he belonged before adding the prestige class level. He does not, however, gain any other benefi t a character of that class would have gained (improved chance of turning or destroying undead, a bonus feat, and so on). If he had more than one spellcasting class before becoming an acolyte of the skin, he must decide to which class to add each level for the purpose of determining spells per day and spells known.	KEY:Acolyte of the Skin ~ Spells per Day																										SORTKEY:Class_Acolyte_Of_The_Skin	SOURCEPAGE:CA	
Wear Fiend	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.AcolyteOfTheSkinClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:An acolyte of the skin summons the essence of a fi end and wears it like a second skin. The bonded fi endish skin is for all intents and purposes the character's own. It increases the acolyte of the skin's natural armor bonus by 1 and grants a +2 inherent bonus to Dexterity. The acolyte also gains darkvision out to 60 feet. The DM determines the actual nature of the skin, be it demonic, devilish, or from some other fi endish creature.	KEY:Acolyte of the Skin ~ Wear Fiend				DEFINE:WearFiendAC|0	DEFINE:WearFiendDarkvision|0				BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Acolyte of the Skin Wear Fiend|1	BONUS:COMBAT|AC|WearFiendAC|TYPE=NaturalArmor.STACK	BONUS:STAT|DEX|2|TYPE=Inherent	BONUS:VAR|DarkvisionRange|WearFiendDarkvision|TYPE=Base	BONUS:VAR|WearFiendAC|1					BONUS:VAR|WearFiendDarkvision|60								SORTKEY:Class_Acolyte_Of_The_Skin	SOURCEPAGE:CA	
