Fiendish Glare	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.AcolyteOfTheSkinClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:From 3rd level on, an acolyte of the skin has the supernatural ability to unnerve opponents with a ferocious glare once per day. This is not a gaze attack, and the target need not meet the acolyte's eyes or even see the acolyte (although the acolyte must have line of effect to the target). Glaring is a standard action that affects any creature the acolyte can see within 100 feet. The target becomes shaken for 10 minutes, and must also attempt a Will save (DC 10 + acolyte's class level + Cha modifi er) or be stunned. The duration of the stun effect depends on the target's hit points:&nl;50 or less 10 rounds&nl;51 to 100 3 rounds&nl;101 to 150 2 rounds&nl;151 or more 1 round&nl;Fiendish glare is a mind-affecting fear effect.	KEY:Acolyte of the Skin ~ Fiendish Glare	DESC:%1 Will or stunned.|FiendishGlareDC			DEFINE:FiendishGlareDC|0					BONUS:VAR|FiendishGlareDC|10+AcolyteOfTheSkinLVL+CHA																	SORTKEY:Class_Acolyte_Of_The_Skin	SOURCEPAGE:CA	
